<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    table, td, th {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 80%;
    }

    td {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .table_padding td {
      padding: 12px;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even){background-color: #f2f2f2}
  </style>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'bootstrap.min.css', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />

</head>
<body>
<div class="container" style="background-color: rgba(242, 242, 242, .33); padding: 0 25px;">
  <div id="header" class=" mb-4">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 mt-2">
        <%= image_tag('MPR.png', style: "width: auto; height: 75px;") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 mt-2">
        <h1>MAAS360</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="content_box">
    <div class="row">
      <span><strong style="font-size: 1.7em;">MDM</strong><span style="font-size: 1.15em"> Zahtjev za ponudom:</span></span>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="row"><b><%= @user %></b>, zaprimili smo Vaš zahtjev za ponudu:</div>
    <table class="table table-striped mt-3">
      <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Naziv paketa</th>
        <th>1 mobitel = 1 korisnik</th>
        <th>1 mobitel = 1 korisnik
        <th style="text-align: right;">Ukupna cijena</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      <tr style="background-color: rgba(34, 168, 173, 0.20);">
        <th scope="row"><%= @package_name.blank? ? '-' : @package_name %></th>
        <td align="center"><%= @one_mobile == '0'? '-' : @one_mobile %></td>
        <td align="center"><%= @multiple_mobile == '0' ? '-' : @multiple_mobile %></td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td></td>
        <td align="center"><%= number_to_currency(@price_one_mobile, unit: 'EUR/mjesečno', separator: ',', format: '%n %u')%></td>
        <td align="center"><%= number_to_currency(@price_multiple_mobile, unit: 'EUR/mjesečno', separator: ',', format: '%n %u')%></td>
        <td align="right"><b><%= number_to_currency(@price_one_mobile+@price_multiple_mobile, unit: 'EUR/mjesečno', separator: ',', format: '%n %u') %></b></td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="row mt-3">Zahvaljujemo Vam se na Vašem upitu!</div>
    <hr>
  </div>
  <div id="footer" class="row mt-3">
    <span><strong style="font-size: 1.35em;">MDM - </strong><span style="color: #b2d043; font-size: 1.25em;"> MaaS360</span></span>
    <p class="mt-2">Ako ste ovu poruku primili greškom ili vam nije namijenjena, ne koristite ju, ne kopirajte, ne distribuirajte, ne otvarajte privitke, odmah ju obrišite sa svog računalnog sustava i obavijestite pošiljatelja da ste to napravili. Hvala!</p>
  </div>
</div>
<script></script>
</body>
</html>